  "prompt": "What is the average salary of IT professional having 10 years experience in India?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, the average salary for IT professionals in India with around 10 years of experience typically ranges from \u20b910 lakhs to \u20b920 lakhs per annum, depending on factors such as the specific technology stack, industry, location (salaries in metropolitan cities like Bangalore, Pune, and Hyderabad tend to be higher), and the size and reputation of the employer.\n\nFor instance, roles like Software Engineer, DevOps Engineer, and Data Scientist at established companies or in high-demand sectors might command salaries on the higher end of that range, while positions in smaller firms may be lower. Additionally, emerging technologies, cloud computing, and AI are particularly lucrative fields in the IT industry.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date information, it\u2019s advisable to consult salary surveys from reputable sources or job portals that provide insights specific to your area of expertise and location.",
